dc:description: Fragment of yellowed woven wool fabric with two very small remnants of purple tapestry, perhaps forming a roundel or oval motif.  One is narrow (0.2 cm x 2.5 cm), the other is 1 cm X 1 cm.  Behind the second section of purple tapestry is a smaller matted/felted piece of yellow wool, possibly, part of the main fragment.
